*
* A small instrument to investigate mesh boxes in a user configuration
* 
* %Description
* Instrument provided by Sam Lambrick from ISIS, that uses three meshes to 
* make their boxes. 
* 
* %Example: Unused_par=1 Detector: PSD_detector_I=10.7752
* 
* %Parameters
* 
* %End 
